{
    "search_spaces": {
        "edgrec-lite-kuairec-search": {
            "description": "Compact KuaiRec_v2 EDGRec search-prior pass over watch-ratio threshold presets, graph-only branch-depth/fanout profiles, negative count, and a small loss-weight grid. Current evidence supports this compact family as a KuaiRec_v2 formal candidate, pending full formal reruns.",
